{
  "title": "What has high fertility got to do with the low birth weight problem in Africa?",
  "abstract": "There has been much concern about adverse individual and societal consequences of high fertility in sub-Saharan Africa. One concern is that children of high birth orders may have low birth weight. However, the evidence for such an effect is not strong.",
